{"tid":377906,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[Audit女娶唔過］不滿友人向男友介紹女性 女會計師帶磚上酒店尋仇","createTime":"2017-08-28T05:30:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-28T13:04:50.000Z","uid":40770,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a05381ea5b7deb64c76dfa4ed9c8f6027abb916f","tid":377906,"uid":40770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T05:30:21.000Z","msg":"不滿友人向男友介紹女性 女會計師帶磚上酒店尋仇<br />\n<br />\n一名女會計師指不滿男友人向其男友介紹女性，在今年6月12日早上於尖沙嘴街頭拾起磚頭，再乘的士到將軍澳香港九龍東皇冠假日酒店房內與男友人算帳，並與於房內的男友爭執。<br />\n<br />\n30歲女會計師葉碧霞被控一項管有攻擊性武器罪，控方昨撤控，改以簽保守行為處理，被告獲准以1,000元守行為一年。<br />\n<br />\n控方案情指，被告當日到達酒店房間後，手持磚頭與男友發生激烈爭執，因而有人報警。被告在警誡下指，涉事的男友人在警方抵達現場前離開。<br />\n<br />\n控方昨撤銷控罪，裁判官告誡被告指「今次好彩」，望被告下次行事前要三思。<br />\n<br />\n我相信只是冰山一角<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170824/57121542\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170824%2F57121542&d=cc5Vyip4F%2BDnLp4ljgfpG6EKYqckrLkk14koP0tj2xA%3D&h=82f610d9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170824%2F57121542&h=77f88558\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170824/57121542</a>"},{"pid":"be939c4bb7716093904aab957c6bb6554a85b28f","tid":377906,"uid":77541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T06:29:08.000Z","msg":"好大壓力咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2c688144b164033fa7ba97ea746ce00a1080261","tid":377906,"uid":51904,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T06:30:41.000Z","msg":"會計師 = auditor?"},{"pid":"a9c91760492d0b55a085b7da34d73671c31b718e","tid":377906,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T06:34:40.000Z","msg":"德勤肥佬黎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"